trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerType" /> class represents the type on which the XML Web service is based.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerType" /> 类表示作为 XML Web services 的基础的类型。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Type" /> on which this XML Web service is based.
trans-unit.target: 作为此 XML Web services 的基础的 <see cref="T:System.Type" />。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WebServiceProtocols" /> value that specifies the transmission protocols that are used to decrypt data sent in the XML Web service request.
trans-unit.target: 一个 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Configuration.WebServiceProtocols" /> 值，它指定用于解密 XML Web services 请求中所发送的数据的传输协议。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerType" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerType" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: The key associated with the desired duplicate <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" />.
trans-unit.target: 与所需的重复的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" /> 关联的键。

trans-unit.source: Returns the duplicate <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" /> associated with the specified key.
trans-unit.target: 返回与指定键关联的重复的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" />。

trans-unit.source: The duplicate <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" /> associated with the specified key.
trans-unit.target: 与指定键相关联的重复的 <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" />。

trans-unit.source: The key associated with the desired <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" />.
Returns the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" /> associated with the specified key.
The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapServerMethod" /> associated with the specified key.
Returns a <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> that indicates whether SOAP data transmissions sent to and from this XML Web service are encoded by default.
trans-unit.target: 返回一个 <see cref="T:System.Boolean" />，它指示默认情况下是否对发送到或源自此 XML Web services 的 SOAP 数据传输进行编码。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if SOAP data transmissions sent to and from this XML Web service are encoded by default; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果默认情况下对发送到或源自此 XML Web services 的 SOAP 数据传输进行编码，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: Gets a <see cref="T:System.String" /> that contains the namespace to which this XML Web service belongs.
trans-unit.target: 获取一个 <see cref="T:System.String" />，其中包含此 XML Web services 所属的命名空间。

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.String" /> that contains the namespace to which this XML Web service belongs.
trans-unit.target: 一个 <see cref="T:System.String" />，其中包含此 XML Web services 所属的命名空间。

trans-unit.source: Returns a <see cref="T:System.Boolean" /> that indicates whether SOAP messages that are routed to this XML Web service are routed based on the <see langword="SOAPAction" /> HTTP header.
trans-unit.target: 返回一个 <see cref="T:System.Boolean" />，它指示路由到此 XML Web services 的 SOAP 消息是否根据 <see langword="SOAPAction" /> HTTP 标头进行路由。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if SOAP messages that are routed to this XML Web service are routed based on the <see langword="SOAPAction" /> HTTP header; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果路由到此 XML Web services 的 SOAP 消息是根据 <see langword="true" /> HTTP 标头进行路由的，则为 <see langword="SOAPAction" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。
